"title": "5431: oaths, divine",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5431: oaths, divine",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Solemn promises made by God to individuals and their offspring. He swears by himself because there is nothing greater to swear by.</p>\n<h2>God swears by himself</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:13-Heb6:14\">HEB 6:13–6:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:16\">GEN 22:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:35\">PSA 89:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:23\">ISA 45:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:8\">ISA 62:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:16-Heb6:18\">HEB 6:16–6:18</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of God's promises by oath</h2>\n<h3>To Abraham</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:15-Gen22:18\">GEN 22:15–22:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:7\">GEN 24:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:3\">GEN 26:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:1\">EXO 33:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:18\">DEU 6:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:8\">DEU 7:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:72-Luke1:73\">LUK 1:72–1:73</a></p>\n<h3>To David</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:11-Ps132:12\">PSA 132:11–132:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam3:9-2Sam3:10\">2SA 3:9–3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:11-2Sam7:16\">2SA 7:11–7:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:3-Ps89:4\">PSA 89:3–89:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:35-Ps89:37\">PSA 89:35–89:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:30\">ACT 2:30</a></p>\n<h3>To his anointed one</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps110:4\">PSA 110:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:17-Heb7:28\">HEB 7:17–7:28</a></p>\n<h3>To the generation in the wilderness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:34-Deut1:36\">DEU 1:34–1:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:20-Num14:35\">NUM 14:20–14:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:10-Heb3:11\">HEB 3:10–3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:10-Ps95:11\">PSA 95:10–95:11</a></p>\n<h3>To Israel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:12-Deut29:15\">DEU 29:12–29:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:8\">EZK 16:8</a></p>",
